title: Rebel Girls CEO on New Book
itunes:title: Rebel Girls CEO on New Book
description:
Jes Wolfe, CEO of Rebel Girls, discusses her book "100 Immigrant Women Who Changed the World." She also talks about the importance of showcasing a broad array of diverse female voices in media.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
